Titolo: Atlantis The Lost Empire: Trial by Fire

Anno: 2001

Descrizione: Atlantis The Lost Empire: Trial by Fire is a movie based video game based on Disney's Atlantis: The Lost Empire. The game was developed by Zombie Studios and published by Disney Interactive. It was released on May 18, 2001 alongside the film exclusively for the Microsoft Windows platform. It is a first-person action-adventure game and is the second of two games developed by Zombie based on the film.